  "description": "Open hi-hat voice given cathedral reverb and maximum decay. The metallic shimmer of a single hat strike sustaining through 3 seconds of room. A second voice at high pitch acts as cymbal wash. Both voices panned slightly apart. XVC hat-choke disabled — hats overlap and bleed. Three voices of pure cymbal radiation.",
